---
title: Kickin’ Chicken Enchilada Bake with Pico de Gallo & Sour Cream
description: These delicious loaded enchiladas have everything you want, and so much of it! You’ll roll up flour tortillas with a supremely satisfying filling of Tex-Mex spiced chicken, green pepper, onion, and tomatoes, top with a savory enchilada sauce, and sprinkle with cheese—then (en)CHILL(ada) while it all bakes in the oven. Finish with fresh pico de gallo and a dollop of sour cream for a hearty meal you can, quite literally, enjoy for days (we sent a lot of food!)

